      "review_summary": "The PR adds optional `heartbeat.fallbacks` support for default and per-agent heartbeat runs, threads explicit fallback overrides through reply-run fallback resolution, and updates related schema/help/tests/docs.\n\nPR surface: Source +37, Tests +107, Docs +6. Total +150 across 19 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. source-level: current main and v2026.6.9 have heartbeat `model` only, with no heartbeat-specific fallback list in schema or runner plumbing. I did not run a live exhausted-provider heartbeat in this read-only review.",
